CHESAPEAKE & O. R. CO. v. PROFFITT. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Fourth Circuit. October 12, 1914.) No. 1247. In Error to the District Court of the United States for the District of Virginia, at Richmond.

BeforePRITCHARD and WOODS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment of District Court affirmed. 218 Fed. 23, 134 C. C. A. 37. Order allowing writ of error to Supreme Court filed.
